                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch adds a new node crash method: node crash is simulated by command executed on the victim nodes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;br/&gt;
      POWER_DOWN=sysrqcrash&lt;br/&gt;
triggers a crash  on all victim nodes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
